body: Honestly, if you didn’t gasp and clutch your chest when Eve gets mad at Nico for telling her to quit and she goes “I know you care about me, we ALL KNOW you care about me, sometimes I think it’s ALL you have” like, I’m gonna doubt you’re gay at all.

summary: Have you ever considered writing a Killing Eve (Eve/Villanelle) fanfic?
question: Have you ever considered writing a Killing Eve (Eve/Villanelle) fanfic?
answer:
Nah. I’m not really into it and plus I’ve written about why I think the psychotic lesbian trope is harmful.


I get why people think it’s hot, though. It’s always fun to fantasize about danger.

blog.name: giantartists
blog.title: Giant Artists
blog.description:
Giant Artists is a full-service agency for artists by artists. We began in March of 2006 and currently represent photographers, illustrators, designers, filmmakers, and one stylist. Giant Artists helps create, nurture, and maintain lasting careers for its artists by curating quality archives and cultural events including public exhibitions and published works. While some of our artists are just beginning their careers, others are award-winning and widely recognized for their excellence and contributions to their fields. We are connected in the spirit of creating art, working with a supportive and innovative community of artists and clients, helping others fulfill their vision, and, simply, making a living doing what we love.

We are inspired by our heroes and fellow risk-takers. Most importantly, we are inspired by each other.
